      <title>中国债券市场上涨，助长杠杆押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/china-s-bond-rally-fuels-leveraged-bets-ahead-of-key-meetings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在对美国潜在关税影响的担忧情绪推动下，中国债券市场历史性上涨可能会促使交易员进行更多杠杆押注，原因是市场预期中国将进一步放松政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/china-s-bond-rally-fuels-leveraged-bets-ahead-of-key-meetings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Dec 2024 05:37:41 GMT</pubDate>
